data.description: Find your flip-flops and get excited for the sand, salt and sea! Your endless summer is here! You will need to look far and wide to find better. Take a short stroll to Bayfront Park Beach & follow the boardwalk for 2 miles to North Beach. Community amenities include FREE access to the  community boat ramp, Bayfront Park & discounted admission to the water park. Step inside to your peaceful yet stylish retreat with everything you ever thought you needed, and find more than you bargained for. Entertain small or large gatherings, formally or informally. Cozy up in the Great Room style  area with a family room, casual dining area and the most amazing kitchen. Relax & enjoy gentle breezes or dine alfresco on a large and nearly maintenance free deck. The lower level offers endless space, a 5th BR and an additional bathroom. The upper level offers 3 spacious bedrooms and an incredible Owner Suite that is larger than most due to the additional bump out area. It boasts an incredible walk in closet that will satisfy any clothes collector and a luxurious bathroom with a soaking tub and shower featuring multiple showerheads; large enough to throw a party in.
